      "text": "輪郭小窓",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781181373,
      "updated": 1781181373
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2aac640000000000d36594",
      "text": "[デライト.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781181541,
      "updated": 1781181546
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2aac640000000000d36595",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781181541,
      "updated": 1781181541
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2aabc00000000000d3658c",
      "text": "輪符にカーソルを合わせると表示させる",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781181377,
      "updated": 1781181409
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2aabe00000000000d3658d",
      "text": " 該当輪郭の内容が表示される",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781181409,
      "updated": 1781181422
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2aabf20000000000d3658e",
      "text": " 上下のプラスボタン/マイナスボタンを使えば引き入れや引き外しなどもできる",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781181427,
      "updated": 1781181694
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2aac190000000000d36592",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781181466,
      "updated": 1781181466
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2aac190000000000d36593",
      "text": "描写内の輪符も前景後景の輪符も対象",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781181466,
      "updated": 1781181497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2aabf20000000000d3658f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781181427,
      "updated": 1781181427
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2aabbd0000000000d3658a",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/f0ab3152aab177d4b7266cbe74dfa93f]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781181373,
      "updated": 1781181374
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2aabbd0000000000d3658b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781181374,
      "updated": 1781181374
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2aac140000000000d36590",
      "text": "[ScrapBubble]に似ている[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781181460,
      "updated": 1781181518
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2abacd00000000007dfc32",
      "text": "これいいよね[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1781185230,
      "updated": 1781185233
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2aac140000000000d36591",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781181460,
      "updated": 1781181460
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b1711000000000082e1cf",
      "text": " 基本[デライト]ばっかり使っていたので[ウィキ]的なツールには大体あるリンクプレビュー機能だと思い込んでいた（[Wikipedia]の影響で）[hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781208888,
      "updated": 1781210424
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b17a4000000000082e1d2",
      "text": "  よくよく観察してみると実はそんなこともない",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781209035,
      "updated": 1781210110
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b1781000000000082e1d1",
      "text": "  [Cosense]に類似機能が無いのが意外だった",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781209000,
      "updated": 1781210025
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b19cf000000000082e1d9",
      "text": "   欲しがる人も多そうだしあって困る機能ではない気がするのだが",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781209590,
      "updated": 1781209607
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b1d6d000000000082e1dc",
      "text": "    [/forum-jp/リンク先のプレビュー機能]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781210516,
      "updated": 1781210516
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b1d6f000000000082e1dd",
      "text": "     要望はあったが反応薄",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781210518,
      "updated": 1781210535
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b1a09000000000082e1da",
      "text": "   簡単な実装なら数時間で出来るレベル",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781209648,
      "updated": 1781209697
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b1a6c000000000082e1db",
      "text": "    実装上面倒なのは小窓向けの表示最適化なのだが、Cosenseはもともとカード向けの表示最適化機能を持っているのでそれを流用すればいい",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781209747,
      "updated": 1781210155
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b1dd3000000000082e1de",
      "text": "   サーバーへのリクエストは増えるがページ全体の取得は抑制できるので特に負荷を上げるものでもない",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781210618,
      "updated": 1781210777
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b1e73000000000082e1df",
      "text": "    プレビュー向けの処理を最小化してキャッシュ周りとか上手く整理できれば",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781210778,
      "updated": 1781210816
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b1719000000000082e1d0",
